Prerequirements:

1) Apache
2) PHP for Apache
3) MySQL (running during the installation)


In order to install this program, you need to run the script install-db, which is found under the
directory bin.
The program will ask you the following questions:

1) The MySQL username
2) The MySQL password for this user
3) The root password, in order to copy files to their destination
4) The directory where the files will me copied. This directory should be visible to apache.

